Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:26.31,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(796,909)}倫巴(Rumba)夜總會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:01:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 你們這群家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 吵死人！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那對咪咪是怎么回事！完全不會晃動嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個假胸妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF64FF&\3c&HD965B5&\blur5}野貓的銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.23,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\pos(742,185)\c&H88FFFE&}三月22日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.23,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\pos(744,282)\c&H88FFFE&}超級飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有熟人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰的熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他會去哪里的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道不錯 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賞個臉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王餐！ 我的鞋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫Rico 是掌管這個貧民區的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶的糾紛都歸我管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你的名字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛！ 不錯嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko... 什么來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合辣妹的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Spicy Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tony(Antonio)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的沖鋒隊隊長Tony君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不認識 那樣的臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不認識？ 你說不認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個臭小鬼的右手 真的不認識嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣？ 能不能想起來啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了啊 Spicy Cat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1... 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3... 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 非常感謝 你想起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認識...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想做無益的殺生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要怎么辦？ 你很想贖罪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金錢嗎？ 肉體勞動也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事Feliciano！ 那種女人有什么好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂！ 無視我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢！ 這件事用錢解決吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tony君的治療費 還有被砸壞的電視的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 你去取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,304房間 明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去的！ 會去的！ 會去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別一個人來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死的 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能這么說...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是擔心你才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻對我說 “會死的 你丫”...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該再稍微考慮一下別人的心情...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來 牽著手回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是昨天的假胸妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的 開！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再敢擋老娘的路 就真的搞死你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人... 好像Michiko小姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.86,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\pos(702,800)\c&H98FDF4&}三月23日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.86,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\pos(704,902)\c&H98FDF4&}超級飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共68Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你是什么關系？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 大概是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那個SB女人是你母親？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找父親嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好男人呢 Hiroshi Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 在夜總會Rumba有個派對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日派對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi君的事情也可以告訴你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hachin 你在啰嗦什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有哦 錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想白吃逃跑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就付錢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:07:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出來！ 全部都放到這里！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hachin 有多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點錢連買煎餃都不夠啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆下地獄去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和SB女人一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么說 你付錢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡搞得太復雜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天那個叫Pepe Lima的女人到飯店去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個像Michiko小姐一樣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個SB女人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人說知道Hiroshi的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她是在說謊 因為她拿著那張肖像畫...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑啊 難道Hiroshi對那個女人下過手？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會 絕對不會！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.46,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(583,738)}三月24日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.46,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(136,926)}Pepe Lima的生日派對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu 不愿意做的話 說出來也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 Lulu會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑吧 Lulu喜歡看到笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pepe 已經座無虛席了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛 不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我穿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你喜歡我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么給我錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一直都在給嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的營業額怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大賺一筆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 Pepe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想對我的收益下手？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是誰的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快樂～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Birthday to Pepe Lima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 請用 請 請
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 聽說你知道Hiroshi的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是想問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的內褲賣了多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便問一下 你現在下面是真空的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道？ 別裝正經
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想賣嗎？ 內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么我要賣內褲啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在看著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢 錢 錢... 都是錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么喜歡錢嗎？ 錢對你那么重要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很喜歡 不過很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么很重要 有多么重要啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有了錢的話 誰都不會嘲笑我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑你？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我他的名字和住址 我會去揍這種家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了 這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人! 絕對還記得！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種謊言可說服不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 說出來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我現在這個樣子 原先我也是正經人家的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都把我當成公主一般對待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 爸爸死了 家里欠了一堆債
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妹妹一起被趕了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一個人出來幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我誰都不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那些人 都是我的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 誰都不會來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太搞笑了 喝果汁能喝成這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說 我和你很像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信別人 更不用說對朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的驚悚故事 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信我說的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不是朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢干什么用？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去Sao Paraiso
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑我的那些人 這下子會被我嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 只要能搞到身份證就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了能做身份證的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就只要去唐人街就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就是進天堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過做兩張的錢還差很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩張？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過吧 我有妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.29,0:14:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人一起獲得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事 一定會成為比我好的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子由我來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 要不要比比酒量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道吧 Hiroshi More... 的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你贏的話 我什么都告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你輸了的話 就給我錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說給我聽聽嗎？ Hiroshi的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi君 是老客人了 讓人頭痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！ 還沒說完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要喝 還要喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們沒有身份證...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Rico把派對賺的錢還給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后為Lulu做張身份證
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再努力一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這里待不下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封鎖所有道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好! 不許讓她們逃出貧民區一步！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人懸賞500Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現后 立刻處死！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu的照片拍的很可愛 想用來做身份證的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的! 為什么我會忘記啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去 去貧民區
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 沒有人知道Lulu的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且Lulu身體很靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巴士車站等我 很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混蛋！ 一定要抓住她！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搶了Rico的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個孩子回去取東西后 就沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你們有身份證的話 就不會變成現在這樣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么！ 不想去？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去過那里嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關我屁事！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要歸罪于別人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那個孩子肯定是出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:18:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想惹麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來以為如果是你的話應該可以信任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 Michiko Malan... 什么的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么辦？ 我可以去叫警察哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣你就麻煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 所以只要你陪我一起到Rico那里就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把錢還回去 帶Lulu走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想Rico不會原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 希望你能稍微幫點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能辦到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想叫就去叫吧 警察
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 為什么不能幫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是這種人？ 我低頭就可以了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也做過約定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我在這里出了事 誰去保護Hatchin？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pepe Lima 你去做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不夠 這么一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不能去幫她...
